  "texts": [
    "The package analyses five types of emotion from the sentences which are happy, angry, surprise, sad, and fear.",
    "The value of each emotion is encoded to 'True', where the value is more than zero, and 'False', where the value is equal to zero.",
    "The highest score among the five emotions is recorded as the label of emotion in the sentences.",
    "Table 9 Sample sentences of sexual harassment with contain sexual harassment words.",
    "He bound my hands and feet and then raped me."
  ]
